metadata.title: Trumpeter Swan Survey - Copper River

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest, Cordova Ranger District

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This data set contains aerial transect data from which trumpeter swan numbers on the Copper River Delta were assessed for 1994. Standard aerial survey method was used flying at 500-600 ft. The purpose of this data is to monitor populations as an indicator of population health, and overall habitat condition.
